home-description: I'm a proactive and detail-oriented software engineering student with a passion for crafting efficient and user-friendly applications. With a strong foundation in software development principles and an eagerness to tackle new challenges, I am seeking freelance opportunities to apply my skills and contribute to innovative projects. My goal is to deliver high-quality solutions that meet the unique needs of each client and exceed their expectations.
about-me-description: I'm a software developer with a focus primarily on backend technologies. I have experience in developing applications using technologies such as SQL Angular, Spring Boot, and Flask. Recently, I have started a project with Solidity, which has allowed me to expand my skills in developing smart contracts and decentralized applications. I excel at designing and implementing efficient, scalable solutions. I enjoy tackling new challenges and learning new technologies to continuously improve my skills as a developer.
